         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Excerpt from land declarations (submitted for the census) of Sabeinos censitor;;Village of Karanis. Herakles and Alexander, both sons of Horion, of the village of Karanis.;     Private land, sown, 6 date-palms therein     44    9/32 ar.;     Royal land, uninundated                                          3 41/64 ar.;     Private land, uninudated, 1 date-palm           18 55/64 ar.;     Royal land, barren                                                         1                ar.;     Private land, sown                                                     37  19/64 ar.;     Private land, uninundated                                       7  45/64 ar."</ab>
